rs and the need to balance change with workload considerations (Meilyr Rowlands, Llyr Gruffydd AM).&#10;&#10;In summary, it is disappointing from this perspective that there has been no significant progress in educational outcomes as reported by Estyn's latest annual report, given the changes and push for self-improvement within the education system. This disappointment arises from a desire to see faster development and progress while balancing the pressures on teachers and workload considerations.">
