enefit from the grant.&#10;&#10;Meilyr Rowlands also points out that there is a lot of jargon around this approach, which might contribute to headteachers' difficulty in understanding it fully. To address this issue, they have produced substantial work explaining the technical terms and providing good examples of their implementation in practice.">
