e-to-one support, monitoring attendance, visiting homes, and bringing agencies into the school to address issues that impact attendance.&#10;&#10;By engaging with the community and families, Cefn Hengoed School has been able to make significant progress in improving attendance for their targeted group of pupils. Their success lies in addressing barriers to learning specific to their students, developing a strong relationship with families, and coordinating efforts with external agencies when necessary.">
